{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Require trauma-informed guidance and training in rape investigations and trials",
        "additional_details": "I feel strongly that the lasting impact of trauma after rape is not properly recognised in rape investigations and trials. I want the justice system to be better informed to help victims.",
        "background": "Require police and prosecutors to have more extensive trauma training to help them consider evidence in rape cases in a trauma-informed way. Include the psychological, physical and functional impact of the offence. Provide guidance to juries on the impact of trauma.",
